app_rpi_img:
	TX: capture image from camera and send to RX, use fork()
	RX: receive image from TX and store to file, use thread
	Change main.txt to main.c, and then use
	
app_fixed_data:
	TX: store a file to array and then send to RX
	RX: receive and temporary store data in array, afterwards write to file
	Test maximum bandwidth